## Tab Notification Clearing

`showTool(toolName, evt)` clears `alertContainer` when switching tabs:
```javascript
function showTool(toolName, evt) {
    const alertContainer = document.getElementById('alertContainer');
    if (alertContainer) alertContainer.innerHTML = '';
    // ... rest of tab switching logic
}
```
This prevents stale "Analysis complete!" banners from showing on unrelated tabs.

